data.description:
The property boasts various ADA accessibility features, such as 36'' doors, roll-in showers, and ADA-compliant countertops. It offers an open floor plan with two main bedroom suites, two secondary bedrooms, and three bathrooms. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless appliances, and a gas stovetop. The house includes amenities like a wood-burning/gas fireplace, porcelain tile flooring, and a commercial carpet for wheelchair ease. The backyard features a large patio and a metal welded cedar fence. The land is situated to the west and behind the fenced area. The property also has features like water softener with a full home filtration system of pristine drinking water. a gas dual heating system, WiFi-operable garage doors, & a U-shaped driveway.
